  "detailed_description": "<br><br>A fast-paced competitive farming game for up to 8 players online! Sabotage and steal while defending your crops and animals to become the best farmer! Team up with others or play on your own!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Plant or steal, your choice!</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1285270/extras/7315c2c669b797b42868be54fe7508a2.poster.avif?t=1746122453\" width=600 height=170 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1285270/extras/7315c2c669b797b42868be54fe7508a2.webm?t=1746122453\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1285270/extras/7315c2c669b797b42868be54fe7508a2.mp4?t=1746122453\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Plant on your farm or steal from your friend, the important thing is to sell as much as possible.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Defend your farm at all costs!</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1285270/extras/eee9483c37ef1a455fd82356e45841c0.poster.avif?t=1746122453\" width=600 height=170 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1285270/extras/eee9483c37ef1a455fd82356e45841c0.webm?t=1746122453\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1285270/extras/eee9483c37ef1a455fd82356e45841c0.mp4?t=1746122453\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Rely on a variety of defensive items to keep invaders away! From scarecrows to electric fences, defensive items can save your crops and animals from a thieving player. Sometimes, the best offense is defense!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Beware of random events!</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1285270/extras/740c919e99561ad7206d876603a74808.poster.avif?t=1746122453\" width=600 height=170 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1285270/extras/740c919e99561ad7206d876603a74808.webm?t=1746122453\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1285270/extras/740c919e99561ad7206d876603a74808.mp4?t=1746122453\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>At every farm, you'll encounter different events that change the game's dynamics – from a shark attack to a treasure hunt, or even a zombie invasion! Just watch out for lightning strikes while you're busy selling your friend's crops!<br><br>The team that accumulates the most coins at the end of the game wins, whether by sabotage or not!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Choose your character!</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1285270/extras/7b75caee8c7a0235cfb163f54f276bdf.poster.avif?t=1746122453\" width=600 height=170 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1285270/extras/7b75caee8c7a0235cfb163f54f276bdf.webm?t=1746122453\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1285270/extras/7b75caee8c7a0235cfb163f54f276bdf.mp4?t=1746122453\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Choose the character that best suits you!",
