oop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1285270/extras/740c919e99561ad7206d876603a74808.poster.avif?t=1746122453\" width=600 height=170 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1285270/extras/740c919e99561ad7206d876603a74808.webm?t=1746122453\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1285270/extras/740c919e99561ad7206d876603a74808.mp4?t=1746122453\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>At every farm, you'll encounter different events that change the game's dynamics – from a shark attack to a treasure hunt, or even a zombie invasion! Just watch out for lightning strikes while you're busy selling your friend's crops!<br><br>The team that accumulates the most coins at the end of the game wins, whether by sabotage or not!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Choose your character!</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1285270/extras/7b75caee8c7a0235cfb163f54f276bdf.poster.avif?t=1746122453\" width=600 height=170 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1285270/extras/7b75caee8c7a0235cfb163f54f276bdf.webm?t=1746122453\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1285270/extras/7b75caee8c7a0235cfb163f54f276bdf.mp4?t=1746122453\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Choose the character that best suits you!",
